### GET all users
GET https://localhost:7266/api/users
Accept: application/json

###

### GET a specific user by ID
GET https://localhost:7266/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

###

### POST create a new user
POST https://localhost:7266/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "johndoe@example.com",
  "role": "Manager"
}

###

### PUT update an existing user
PUT https://localhost:7266/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "John Smith",
  "email": "johnsmith@example.com",
  "role": "Administrator"
}

###

### DELETE a user by ID
DELETE https://localhost:7266/api/users/1

